{"tid":2129491,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新西蘭外長：不再相信香港刑事司法系統完全獨立於中國，一國兩制被破壞，將香港視為中國","createTime":"2020-07-28T15:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:02:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"784eb915b8dc41563a7c7c9381cd1656a59a7e3a","tid":2129491,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/紐西蘭中止-引渡條例-不再相信香港司法獨立於中國-012236731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E4%B8%AD%E6%AD%A2-%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E7%9B%B8%E4%BF%A1%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-012236731.html&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDylkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=38ee1897\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/紐西蘭中止-引渡條例-不再相信香港司法獨立於中國-012236731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wGZ6jiLYevm8nVkB9fXtlA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/ctwant_com_582/30cae04d3025805dc098aa66af61f3b6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwGZ6jiLYevm8nVkB9fXtlA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fctwant_com_582%2F30cae04d3025805dc098aa66af61f3b6&h=6da174b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國強推「港版國安法」後引發國際間一片撻伐，包含美國、英國、加拿大以及澳洲都宣布暫停對香港的引渡條例，如今紐西蘭副總理及外交大臣特斯（Winston Peters）也表示，不再相信香港司法獨立於中國，因此做出相同的決定，中止引渡條例。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，皮特斯說：「中國通過新的國家安全立法，已經削弱了法治原則，破壞了香港獨特地位一國兩制的框架，並違背了中國對國際社會所作的承諾。」正因如此，紐西蘭打算對此做出反制。<br />\n<br />\n皮特斯繼續說：「作為回應的一部分，內閣決定中止紐西蘭與香港的引渡條例，紐西蘭再也不能相信香港的刑事司法系統完全獨立於中國。」<br />\n<br />\n由於「港版國安法」引起國際間的憂慮，紐西蘭也升級對香港的旅遊警示，同時將香港視為中國，軍事、民軍兩用的貨物和科技出口方面，採取相同的規範。"},{"pid":"4343fb4d2ddac8c9d474ebe45a05c8bf855080a3","tid":2129491,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28c74b194013062c2dda05177fc71d9a0f289d8","tid":2129491,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭"},{"pid":"f35e6fe26c29b1b25e3e5786fca9ad6c1d27a221","tid":2129491,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:52:21.000Z","msg":"咁幾時撤回新西蘭法官先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82c214fa1ca5861e8618fddb572b8d25a5dbf9d","tid":2129491,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244ceeab6d255e8e17dc3e369b46842c673bca86","tid":2129491,"uid":326287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8eda2869896d39172362533def71e6f5e1da2b0c","tid":2129491,"uid":361751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qn4sJ1b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqn4sJ1b.gif&h=edea6cfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed831434d2dfecc4c22c7cf5f837158c99aafd05","tid":2129491,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eda2869896d39172362533def71e6f5e1da2b0c","tid":2129491,"uid":361751,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qn4sJ1b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.c